<br>
Mailing cost?  Not even $.10 a piece, and a total cost of maybe $250m to design, fabricate, and mass mail.<br>
<br>
Laying off 300 ppl.<br>
<br>
Ok, simple terms:<br>
<br>
Each person makes $30m (m=Roman Numeral for thousand), times 300 ppl is NINE MILLION DOLLARS.  $30m a year is just about $15 an hour.<br>
<br>
Then you have the direct costs associated with 300 employees.  Health Insurance, for example.  Unless you are paying for 100% of the insurance premium yourself, the company foots some of the bill.  My company pays 100% of my families health insurance, which is about $12m a year (going to use this amount for the example yours may be higher or lower, etc. btw for those of you playing at home, it's $993/month for health insurance)<br>
<br>
So, let's say your company pays ony 50% of your total insurance bill, and the rest is what they take out of your check.  $6m times 300ppl, $1.8mm.  Not to mention workman's comp insurance, long-term disability, short-term disability, FICA taxes, and the other misc. expenses that companies have incurr, in order to employ 300 ppl, is roughly about $4m ($4,000 a year is only about $15 a day, or $75 a week) per person annually.  So, 300 ppl go bye-bye, you add another $3mm to the EBITA.<br>
<br>
So, by just those numbers alone, if you company can do the same volume of work with 300 less enployees, your company will save almost TWELVE MILLION DOLLARS.<br>
<br>
If the company did $120mm in Gross Revenue, and you take $12mm off the G&amp;A expenses (this is where payroll/salary and other general and administrative costs go on a P &amp; L statement), you have added almost 10% of net revenue (EBITA) that wasn't there before.<br>
<br>
If you could add 10% to the profit of your company, you would be a hero.<br>
<br>
That's why no one gave a shit about the glossy mailing. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.maine.rr.com/waassaap/newtag.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/bdrinal28133.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tatianaefatecaster>Tatianae Fatecaster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>No Life</span><br>  Posts: 1384<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/15/02 12:32:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1655.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ..</span><hr size=1> Another good reason to not vote Republican or Libertarian right now =0 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/bdrinal28133.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tatianaefatecaster>Tatianae Fatecaster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>No Life</span><br>  Posts: 1385<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/15/02 12:42:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1655.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ...</span><hr size=1> Sorb please redo your math to 6,300 employees not 300. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/bdrinal28133.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dirrabey>Dirra Bey</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>No Life</span><br>  Posts: 2426<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/15/02 12:44:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreen